Story: Girl thinks she's perfect, tries to get it on with the basketball captain during festival, but he rejects her. Storms off angry, trips and breaks her sandal, rugby guy (gorilla) helps her up and gives her his sandals. She ends up falling for him and follows him for several days trying to return his sandals and when she does she asks him out but he's too busy and goes off with another girl. Perfect girl thinks he likes that girl instead and tries to seduce him but gorilla stops her and she snaps. He clarifies that girl was just the rugby manager, they make up and have sex afterwards with gorilla asking perfect girl out this time.
